{"tid":1012843,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"台女好心借錢助改機票 港男登機後即玩失蹤","createTime":"2019-02-08T01:38:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-08T03:35:09.000Z","uid":56881,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f9c61450ddbc9581cf5a5a4f425a3916bdda3c9d","tid":1012843,"uid":56881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T01:38:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%8F%B0%E5%A5%B3%E5%A5%BD%E5%BF%83%E5%80%9F%E9%8C%A2%E5%8A%A9%E6%94%B9%E6%A9%9F%E7%A5%A8%E3%80%80%E6%B8%AF%E7%94%B7%E7%99%BB%E6%A9%9F%E5%BE%8C%E5%8D%B3%E7%8E%A9%E5%A4%B1%E8%B9%A4-234218968.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%258F%25B0%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%25A5%25BD%25E5%25BF%2583%25E5%2580%259F%25E9%258C%25A2%25E5%258A%25A9%25E6%2594%25B9%25E6%25A9%259F%25E7%25A5%25A8%25E3%2580%2580%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%2594%25B7%25E7%2599%25BB%25E6%25A9%259F%25E5%25BE%258C%25E5%258D%25B3%25E7%258E%25A9%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E8%25B9%25A4-234218968.html&d=HNFwsad0YdNlvWXbC%2BF%2BctUsrLV3ynd9sCeqRx8pZcg%3D&h=fbcd58ca\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%8F%B0%E5%A5%B3%E5%A5%BD%E5%BF%83%E5%80%9F%E9%8C%A2%E5%8A%A9%E6%94%B9%E6%A9%9F%E7%A5%A8%E3%80%80%E6%B8%AF%E7%94%B7%E7%99%BB%E6%A9%9F%E5%BE%8C%E5%8D%B3%E7%8E%A9%E5%A4%B1%E8%B9%A4-234218968.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/UVQC3K1AQteEzF402FknBQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzgwO2g9NTU3/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/1c5b3c99b017763e367fad20450ac444\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FUVQC3K1AQteEzF402FknBQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzgwO2g9NTU3%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2F1c5b3c99b017763e367fad20450ac444&h=1e8d1797&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好心幫人反被騙？台灣一名女網民周四（7日）在Facebook群組「爆料公社」發文，指上月25日好心幫助一名自稱「羅先生」的香港人，借了6000元（新台幣．下同，約1550港元）予對方購買機票；豈料「羅先生」登機後，竟封鎖了她的Fb並消聲匿迹，令她不禁自嘲：「我知道可能會有人說我笨，自找麻煩！但我覺得我好心幫助香港人，換來的是這樣的結果，真心覺得很失望！」<br />\n<br />\n該女網民透露，事發於上月25日下午6時許，她當時在台北車站往機場捷運方向，遇上「羅先生」。女網民聽到「羅先生」語氣緊張地與朋友訴說「東西被偷，無法回港」，基於自己男友亦是香港人，便好心上前詢問是否需要幫忙。對方指其手袋、護照、台幣、港幣通通被偷，「香港急難救助單位說能幫助他改機票讓他今晚能回香港，改機票費用約4000台幣」。由於女網民上月30日會飛到香港尋找男友，她便主動相借6000元，對方承諾待她飛到香港後，便會歸還。<br />\n<br />\n雖然「羅先生」留下了電話號碼和即時通訊軟件的聯絡方法，且在登機前一直與女網民保持聯繫，但當他回到香港後，便封鎖了所有聯繫方法。女網民看見對方把自己封鎖，感到十分失望，便留言說︰「我真心幫助你，結果你卻欺騙我。」其後，該女網民找到「羅先生」的Fb資料，並將該些資料發布到「爆料公社」，直言「這1500港幣對我來說不是筆小錢，我希望能拿得回來，也希望這個已經當爸爸的X先生，不要給你的孩子做了最差的示範！」<br />\n<br />\n東網記者曾嘗試按Fb上的聯繫資料，試圖聯絡該女網民及「港男」，惟暫時未有回應。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 影衰哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3029d3a4138d8483ec9ebbc24da5fac2f21f46b","tid":1012843,"uid":86756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T02:02:41.000Z","msg":"遇上「羅先生」。女網民聽到<span style=\"color: red;\">「羅先生」</span>語氣緊張地與朋友訴說「東西被偷，無法回港」，基於自己男友亦是香港人，便好心上前詢問是否需要幫忙。對方指其<span style=\"color: red;\">手袋</span>、護照、台幣、港幣通通被偷"},{"pid":"d6e797ba19753ce6d797d4343e54d5b1439cdcf6","tid":1012843,"uid":51701,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T02:04:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K8m5Pa4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK8m5Pa4.jpg&h=1a0e8216&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6505947341d4701fd11b7d861cc5dead2de45099","tid":1012843,"uid":83354,"like":1,"dislike":12,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T02:09:53.000Z","msg":"抵撚死啦台狗"},{"pid":"2ba259e01efd461f4a7ed47cbd9d886a7132e987","tid":1012843,"uid":172507,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6505947341d4701fd11b7d861cc5dead2de45099","tid":1012843,"uid":83354,"like":1,"dislike":12,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T02:09:53.000Z","msg":"抵撚死啦台狗"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T02:18:45.000Z","msg":"人地好心幫你都咁撚樣講嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /